"- region \"Booking flow masthead\":\n  - text: Vecells Booking_Flow_Contract_Atlas\n  - paragraph: Search, ranking, reservation, commit, confirmation, and manage truth are frozen here as one bounded contract pack.\n  - text: 280.phase4.booking-flow-freeze.v1\n- complementary \"Booking flow stage rail\":\n  - heading \"Flow stages\" [level=2]\n  - button \"Search snapshot 6 Search is a snapshot-producing operation. Selection and commit consume persisted snapshot truth, not live supplier lists.\":\n    - strong: Search snapshot\n    - text: 6 Search is a snapshot-producing operation. Selection and commit consume persisted snapshot truth, not live supplier lists.\n  - button \"Ranking frontier 1 Hard filters run before a versioned rank plan computes frontier-safe soft reordering inside clinically bounded timeliness bands.\":\n    - strong: Ranking frontier\n    - text: 1 Hard filters run before a versioned rank plan computes frontier-safe soft reordering inside clinically bounded timeliness bands.\n  - button \"Offer session 2 OfferSession binds selected candidates, rank proof, and one current reservation-truth projection without implying exclusivity from session TTL alone.\":\n    - strong: Offer session\n    - text: 2 OfferSession binds selected candidates, rank proof, and one current reservation-truth projection without implying exclusivity from session TTL alone.\n  - button \"Reservation truth 1 Reserved wording, hold countdowns, and truthful nonexclusive posture can render only from ReservationTruthProjection.\":\n    - strong: Reservation truth\n    - text: 1 Reserved wording, hold countdowns, and truthful nonexclusive posture can render only from ReservationTruthProjection.\n  - button \"Commit revalidation 2 Commit separates local acknowledgement, processing acceptance, external observation, and authoritative outcome, and it fails closed on stale route, policy, or supplier truth.\":\n    - strong: Commit revalidation\n    - text: 2 Commit separates local acknowledgement, processing acceptance, external observation, and authoritative outcome, and it fails closed on stale route, policy, or supplier truth.\n  - button \"Confirmation truth 1 Booked summary, manage, artifact, and reminder exposure appear only when confirmation truth is confirmed with durable proof or same-commit read-after-write.\" [pressed]:\n    - strong: Confirmation truth\n    - text: 1 Booked summary, manage, artifact, and reminder exposure appear only when confirmation truth is confirmed with durable proof or same-commit read-after-write.\n  - button \"Manage continuity 1 Manage exposure depends on current capability, continuity evidence, and route writability, not on page shape or appointment presence.\":\n    - strong: Manage continuity\n    - text: 1 Manage exposure depends on current capability, continuity evidence, and route writability, not on page shape or appointment presence.\n  - button \"Waitlist and fallback 2 No-supply, expired offer, and failed commit branches already depend on typed waitlist and fallback truth, so those seams are frozen now.\":\n    - strong: Waitlist and fallback\n    - text: 2 No-supply, expired offer, and failed commit branches already depend on typed waitlist and fallback truth, so those seams are frozen now.\n  - heading \"Formula rail\" [level=2]\n  - button \"SnapshotSelectable(q,t) expiresAt, caseVersionRef, policyBundleHash\":\n    - strong: SnapshotSelectable(q,t)\n    - text: expiresAt, caseVersionRef, policyBundleHash\n  - button \"windowClass(s) preferredWindowStartAt, preferredWindowEndAt, acceptableWindowStartAt\":\n    - strong: windowClass(s)\n    - text: preferredWindowStartAt, preferredWindowEndAt, acceptableWindowStartAt\n  - button \"Frontier_b windowClass, startAtEpoch, earliestStart_b\":\n    - strong: Frontier_b\n    - text: windowClass, startAtEpoch, earliestStart_b\n  - button \"softScore(s) w_delay, w_continuity, w_site\":\n    - strong: softScore(s)\n    - text: w_delay, w_continuity, w_site\n  - button \"RevalidationPass(tx,t) snapshotId, providerAdapterBindingHash, selectedSlotRef\":\n    - strong: RevalidationPass(tx,t)\n    - text: snapshotId, providerAdapterBindingHash, selectedSlotRef\n  - button \"RouteWritable(tx,t) surfaceRouteContractRef, surfacePublicationRef, runtimePublicationBundleRef\" [pressed]:\n    - strong: RouteWritable(tx,t)\n    - text: surfaceRouteContractRef, surfacePublicationRef, runtimePublicationBundleRef\n  - button \"Cancelable(a,t) appointmentStatus, startAt, cancelCutoff\":\n    - strong: Cancelable(a,t)\n    - text: appointmentStatus, startAt, cancelCutoff\n  - button \"Reschedulable(a,t) appointmentStatus, startAt, amendCutoff\":\n    - strong: Reschedulable(a,t)\n    - text: appointmentStatus, startAt, amendCutoff\n- region \"Booking flow atlas canvas\":\n  - heading \"Snapshot pipeline\" [level=3]\n  - strong: Search snapshot\n  - text: Search is a snapshot-producing operation. Selection and commit consume persisted snapshot truth, not live supplier lists.\n  - strong: Ranking frontier\n  - text: Hard filters run before a versioned rank plan computes frontier-safe soft reordering inside clinically bounded timeliness bands.\n  - strong: Offer session\n  - text: OfferSession binds selected candidates, rank proof, and one current reservation-truth projection without implying exclusivity from session TTL alone.\n  - table \"Snapshot pipeline table\":\n    - rowgroup:\n      - row \"Stage Purpose\":\n        - columnheader \"Stage\"\n        - columnheader \"Purpose\"\n    - rowgroup:\n      - row \"Search snapshot Search is a snapshot-producing operation. Selection and commit consume persisted snapshot truth, not live supplier lists.\":\n        - cell \"Search snapshot\"\n        - cell \"Search is a snapshot-producing operation. Selection and commit consume persisted snapshot truth, not live supplier lists.\"\n      - row \"Ranking frontier Hard filters run before a versioned rank plan computes frontier-safe soft reordering inside clinically bounded timeliness bands.\":\n        - cell \"Ranking frontier\"\n        - cell \"Hard filters run before a versioned rank plan computes frontier-safe soft reordering inside clinically bounded timeliness bands.\"\n      - row \"Offer session OfferSession binds selected candidates, rank proof, and one current reservation-truth projection without implying exclusivity from session TTL alone.\":\n        - cell \"Offer session\"\n        - cell \"OfferSession binds selected candidates, rank proof, and one current reservation-truth projection without implying exclusivity from session TTL alone.\"\n  - heading \"Ranking frontier rail\" [level=3]\n  - strong: windowClass(s)\n  - text: windowClass(s) = 2 for inside clinically preferred window, 1 for inside clinically acceptable window, 0 for outside window\n  - strong: Frontier_b\n  - text: \"Frontier_b = { s : windowClass(s)=b and startAtEpoch(s) <= earliestStart_b + Delta_reorder_b }\"\n  - strong: softScore(s)\n  - text: softScore(s) = w_delay * f_delay(s) + w_continuity * f_continuity(s) + w_site * f_site(s) + w_tod * f_tod(s) + w_travel * f_travel(s) + w_modality * f_modality(s)\n  - table \"Ranking frontier table\":\n    - rowgroup:\n      - row \"Formula Use\":\n        - columnheader \"Formula\"\n        - columnheader \"Use\"\n    - rowgroup:\n      - row \"windowClass(s) windowClass(s) = 2 for inside clinically preferred window, 1 for inside clinically acceptable window, 0 for outside window\":\n        - cell \"windowClass(s)\"\n        - cell \"windowClass(s) = 2 for inside clinically preferred window, 1 for inside clinically acceptable window, 0 for outside window\"\n      - 'row \"Frontier_b Frontier_b = { s : windowClass(s)=b and startAtEpoch(s) <= earliestStart_b + Delta_reorder_b }\"':\n        - cell \"Frontier_b\"\n        - 'cell \"Frontier_b = { s : windowClass(s)=b and startAtEpoch(s) <= earliestStart_b + Delta_reorder_b }\"'\n      - row \"softScore(s) softScore(s) = w_delay * f_delay(s) + w_continuity * f_continuity(s) + w_site * f_site(s) + w_tod * f_tod(s) + w_travel * f_travel(s) + w_modality * f_modality(s)\":\n        - cell \"softScore(s)\"\n        - cell \"softScore(s) = w_delay * f_delay(s) + w_continuity * f_continuity(s) + w_site * f_site(s) + w_tod * f_tod(s) + w_travel * f_travel(s) + w_modality * f_modality(s)\"\n  - heading \"Reservation truth ladder\" [level=3]\n  - strong: exclusive_held\n  - text: Real held reservation with lawful hold countdown.\n  - strong: truthful_nonexclusive\n  - text: Selected offer is still subject to live confirmation.\n  - strong: pending_confirmation\n  - text: Capacity claim is preserved while booking confirmation is still pending.\n  - strong: confirmed\n  - text: Reservation and booking truth have converged.\n  - strong: disputed\n  - text: Supplier or callback truth is contradictory.\n  - strong: released\n  - text: Previously visible claim is released.\n  - strong: expired\n  - text: Previously visible claim expired.\n  - strong: revalidation_required\n  - text: Snapshot or route truth drifted and must refresh.\n  - strong: unavailable\n  - text: Capacity is no longer safely claimable.\n  - table \"Reservation truth table\":\n    - rowgroup:\n      - row \"Truth state Meaning\":\n        - columnheader \"Truth state\"\n        - columnheader \"Meaning\"\n    - rowgroup:\n      - row \"exclusive_held Real held reservation with lawful hold countdown.\":\n        - cell \"exclusive_held\"\n        - cell \"Real held reservation with lawful hold countdown.\"\n      - row \"truthful_nonexclusive Selected offer is still subject to live confirmation.\":\n        - cell \"truthful_nonexclusive\"\n        - cell \"Selected offer is still subject to live confirmation.\"\n      - row \"pending_confirmation Capacity claim is preserved while booking confirmation is still pending.\":\n        - cell \"pending_confirmation\"\n        - cell \"Capacity claim is preserved while booking confirmation is still pending.\"\n      - row \"confirmed Reservation and booking truth have converged.\":\n        - cell \"confirmed\"\n        - cell \"Reservation and booking truth have converged.\"\n      - row \"disputed Supplier or callback truth is contradictory.\":\n        - cell \"disputed\"\n        - cell \"Supplier or callback truth is contradictory.\"\n      - row \"released Previously visible claim is released.\":\n        - cell \"released\"\n        - cell \"Previously visible claim is released.\"\n      - row \"expired Previously visible claim expired.\":\n        - cell \"expired\"\n        - cell \"Previously visible claim expired.\"\n      - row \"revalidation_required Snapshot or route truth drifted and must refresh.\":\n        - cell \"revalidation_required\"\n        - cell \"Snapshot or route truth drifted and must refresh.\"\n      - row \"unavailable Capacity is no longer safely claimable.\":\n        - cell \"unavailable\"\n        - cell \"Capacity is no longer safely claimable.\"\n  - heading \"Confirmation truth ladder\" [level=3]\n  - strong: booking_in_progress\n  - text: Local acknowledgement or dispatch may exist, but final truth is unresolved.\n  - strong: confirmation_pending\n  - text: External or weak confirmation is still pending.\n  - strong: reconciliation_required\n  - text: Contradictory or ambiguous confirmation needs governed recovery.\n  - strong: confirmed\n  - text: Booked summary, manage, artifacts, and reminders may widen according to exposure state.\n  - strong: failed\n  - text: Booking failed and must stay in recovery posture.\n  - strong: expired\n  - text: Pending confirmation timed out.\n  - strong: superseded\n  - text: A newer transaction or lineage superseded this projection.\n  - table \"Confirmation truth table\":\n    - rowgroup:\n      - row \"Truth state Meaning\":\n        - columnheader \"Truth state\"\n        - columnheader \"Meaning\"\n    - rowgroup:\n      - row \"booking_in_progress Local acknowledgement or dispatch may exist, but final truth is unresolved.\":\n        - cell \"booking_in_progress\"\n        - cell \"Local acknowledgement or dispatch may exist, but final truth is unresolved.\"\n      - row \"confirmation_pending External or weak confirmation is still pending.\":\n        - cell \"confirmation_pending\"\n        - cell \"External or weak confirmation is still pending.\"\n      - row \"reconciliation_required Contradictory or ambiguous confirmation needs governed recovery.\":\n        - cell \"reconciliation_required\"\n        - cell \"Contradictory or ambiguous confirmation needs governed recovery.\"\n      - row \"confirmed Booked summary, manage, artifacts, and reminders may widen according to exposure state.\":\n        - cell \"confirmed\"\n        - cell \"Booked summary, manage, artifacts, and reminders may widen according to exposure state.\"\n      - row \"failed Booking failed and must stay in recovery posture.\":\n        - cell \"failed\"\n        - cell \"Booking failed and must stay in recovery posture.\"\n      - row \"expired Pending confirmation timed out.\":\n        - cell \"expired\"\n        - cell \"Pending confirmation timed out.\"\n      - row \"superseded A newer transaction or lineage superseded this projection.\":\n        - cell \"superseded\"\n        - cell \"A newer transaction or lineage superseded this projection.\"\n  - heading \"Manage-state matrix\" [level=3]\n  - table \"Manage-state matrix\":\n    - rowgroup:\n      - row \"Settlement result Meaning\":\n        - columnheader \"Settlement result\"\n        - columnheader \"Meaning\"\n    - rowgroup:\n      - row \"applied Manage mutation applied and authoritative continuity still validates.\":\n        - cell \"applied\"\n        - cell \"Manage mutation applied and authoritative continuity still validates.\"\n      - row \"supplier_pending Manage mutation is accepted locally but still waiting on supplier truth.\":\n        - cell \"supplier_pending\"\n        - cell \"Manage mutation is accepted locally but still waiting on supplier truth.\"\n      - row \"stale_recoverable Refresh or reconcile before another ordinary mutation.\":\n        - cell \"stale_recoverable\"\n        - cell \"Refresh or reconcile before another ordinary mutation.\"\n      - row \"unsupported_capability Current route, supplier, or audience cannot perform the requested manage action.\":\n        - cell \"unsupported_capability\"\n        - cell \"Current route, supplier, or audience cannot perform the requested manage action.\"\n      - row \"safety_preempted Clinical content must route back into governed request review.\":\n        - cell \"safety_preempted\"\n        - cell \"Clinical content must route back into governed request review.\"\n      - row \"reconciliation_required Supplier or continuity truth is contradictory.\":\n        - cell \"reconciliation_required\"\n        - cell \"Supplier or continuity truth is contradictory.\"\n  - heading \"Formula ledger\" [level=3]\n  - table \"Formula ledger\":\n    - rowgroup:\n      - row \"Formula Expression Fields\":\n        - columnheader \"Formula\"\n        - columnheader \"Expression\"\n        - columnheader \"Fields\"\n    - rowgroup:\n      - 'row \"SnapshotSelectable(q,t) SnapshotSelectable(q,t) = 1[t <= q.expiresAt] * 1[q.caseVersionRef matches the active BookingCase version] * 1[q.policyBundleHash matches the active compiled policy bundle] * 1[q.providerAdapterBindingHash matches the current BookingCapabilityResolution.providerAdapterBindingHash] * 1[q.capabilityTupleHash matches the current BookingCapabilityResolution.capabilityTupleHash] * 1[q.coverageState in {complete, partial_coverage}] * 1[recoveryState(q).viewState != stale_refresh_required] expiresAt, caseVersionRef, policyBundleHash, providerAdapterBindingHash, capabilityTupleHash, coverageState, recoveryState.viewState\"':\n        - cell \"SnapshotSelectable(q,t)\"\n        - 'cell \"SnapshotSelectable(q,t) = 1[t <= q.expiresAt] * 1[q.caseVersionRef matches the active BookingCase version] * 1[q.policyBundleHash matches the active compiled policy bundle] * 1[q.providerAdapterBindingHash matches the current BookingCapabilityResolution.providerAdapterBindingHash] * 1[q.capabilityTupleHash matches the current BookingCapabilityResolution.capabilityTupleHash] * 1[q.coverageState in {complete, partial_coverage}] * 1[recoveryState(q).viewState != stale_refresh_required]\"'\n        - cell \"expiresAt, caseVersionRef, policyBundleHash, providerAdapterBindingHash, capabilityTupleHash, coverageState, recoveryState.viewState\"\n      - row \"windowClass(s) windowClass(s) = 2 for inside clinically preferred window, 1 for inside clinically acceptable window, 0 for outside window preferredWindowStartAt, preferredWindowEndAt, acceptableWindowStartAt, acceptableWindowEndAt, slotStartAtEpoch\":\n        - cell \"windowClass(s)\"\n        - cell \"windowClass(s) = 2 for inside clinically preferred window, 1 for inside clinically acceptable window, 0 for outside window\"\n        - cell \"preferredWindowStartAt, preferredWindowEndAt, acceptableWindowStartAt, acceptableWindowEndAt, slotStartAtEpoch\"\n      - 'row \"Frontier_b Frontier_b = { s : windowClass(s)=b and startAtEpoch(s) <= earliestStart_b + Delta_reorder_b } windowClass, startAtEpoch, earliestStart_b, Delta_reorder_b\"':\n        - cell \"Frontier_b\"\n        - 'cell \"Frontier_b = { s : windowClass(s)=b and startAtEpoch(s) <= earliestStart_b + Delta_reorder_b }\"'\n        - cell \"windowClass, startAtEpoch, earliestStart_b, Delta_reorder_b\"\n      - row \"softScore(s) softScore(s) = w_delay * f_delay(s) + w_continuity * f_continuity(s) + w_site * f_site(s) + w_tod * f_tod(s) + w_travel * f_travel(s) + w_modality * f_modality(s) w_delay, w_continuity, w_site, w_tod, w_travel, w_modality, f_delay, f_continuity, f_site, f_tod, f_travel, f_modality\":\n        - cell \"softScore(s)\"\n        - cell \"softScore(s) = w_delay * f_delay(s) + w_continuity * f_continuity(s) + w_site * f_site(s) + w_tod * f_tod(s) + w_travel * f_travel(s) + w_modality * f_modality(s)\"\n        - cell \"w_delay, w_continuity, w_site, w_tod, w_travel, w_modality, f_delay, f_continuity, f_site, f_tod, f_travel, f_modality\"\n      - row \"RevalidationPass(tx,t) RevalidationPass(tx,t) = SnapshotSelectable(SlotSetSnapshot(tx.snapshotId),t) * 1[tx.providerAdapterBindingHash matches the current BookingCapabilityResolution.providerAdapterBindingHash] * LiveSupplierBookable(tx.selectedSlotRef,t) * PolicySatisfied(tx.selectedSlotRef, tx.policyBundleHash) * RouteWritable(tx,t) * VersionFresh(tx.preflightVersion, tx.selectedSlotRef, t) snapshotId, providerAdapterBindingHash, selectedSlotRef, policyBundleHash, preflightVersion, routeIntentBindingRef, surfacePublicationRef, runtimePublicationBundleRef\":\n        - cell \"RevalidationPass(tx,t)\"\n        - cell \"RevalidationPass(tx,t) = SnapshotSelectable(SlotSetSnapshot(tx.snapshotId),t) * 1[tx.providerAdapterBindingHash matches the current BookingCapabilityResolution.providerAdapterBindingHash] * LiveSupplierBookable(tx.selectedSlotRef,t) * PolicySatisfied(tx.selectedSlotRef, tx.policyBundleHash) * RouteWritable(tx,t) * VersionFresh(tx.preflightVersion, tx.selectedSlotRef, t)\"\n        - cell \"snapshotId, providerAdapterBindingHash, selectedSlotRef, policyBundleHash, preflightVersion, routeIntentBindingRef, surfacePublicationRef, runtimePublicationBundleRef\"\n      - row \"RouteWritable(tx,t) RouteWritable(tx,t) = 1[AudienceSurfaceRouteContract live and surface publication current and RuntimePublicationBundle live and PatientShellConsistencyProjection valid and, when embedded, PatientEmbeddedSessionProjection valid] surfaceRouteContractRef, surfacePublicationRef, runtimePublicationBundleRef, patientShellConsistencyProjectionRef, patientEmbeddedSessionProjectionRef\":\n        - cell \"RouteWritable(tx,t)\"\n        - cell \"RouteWritable(tx,t) = 1[AudienceSurfaceRouteContract live and surface publication current and RuntimePublicationBundle live and PatientShellConsistencyProjection valid and, when embedded, PatientEmbeddedSessionProjection valid]\"\n        - cell \"surfaceRouteContractRef, surfacePublicationRef, runtimePublicationBundleRef, patientShellConsistencyProjectionRef, patientEmbeddedSessionProjectionRef\"\n      - row \"Cancelable(a,t) Cancelable(a,t) = 1[a.status = booked and startAt(a) - t >= cancelCutoff(a) and no live AppointmentManageCommand fence exists for a] appointmentStatus, startAt, cancelCutoff, liveCommandFence\":\n        - cell \"Cancelable(a,t)\"\n        - cell \"Cancelable(a,t) = 1[a.status = booked and startAt(a) - t >= cancelCutoff(a) and no live AppointmentManageCommand fence exists for a]\"\n        - cell \"appointmentStatus, startAt, cancelCutoff, liveCommandFence\"\n      - row \"Reschedulable(a,t) Reschedulable(a,t) = 1[a.status = booked and startAt(a) - t >= amendCutoff(a) and no live AppointmentManageCommand fence exists for a] appointmentStatus, startAt, amendCutoff, liveCommandFence\":\n        - cell \"Reschedulable(a,t)\"\n        - cell \"Reschedulable(a,t) = 1[a.status = booked and startAt(a) - t >= amendCutoff(a) and no live AppointmentManageCommand fence exists for a]\"\n        - cell \"appointmentStatus, startAt, amendCutoff, liveCommandFence\"\n  - heading \"Contract split\" [level=3]\n  - table \"Contract split table\":\n    - rowgroup:\n      - row \"Contract Authority Reason\":\n        - columnheader \"Contract\"\n        - columnheader \"Authority\"\n        - columnheader \"Reason\"\n    - rowgroup:\n      - row \"SlotSearchSession Snapshot-producing search session, fenced to case version, policy bundle, capability tuple, and adapter binding keeps live supplier lists from leaking directly into selection or commit\":\n        - cell \"SlotSearchSession\"\n        - cell \"Snapshot-producing search session, fenced to case version, policy bundle, capability tuple, and adapter binding\"\n        - cell \"keeps live supplier lists from leaking directly into selection or commit\"\n      - row \"ProviderSearchSlice per-provider coverage, degradation, and raw payload lineage distinguishes complete, partial, timeout, and degraded coverage\":\n        - cell \"ProviderSearchSlice\"\n        - cell \"per-provider coverage, degradation, and raw payload lineage\"\n        - cell \"distinguishes complete, partial, timeout, and degraded coverage\"\n      - row \"TemporalNormalizationEnvelope timezone, DST, and clock-skew correctness prevents supplier-local timestamps from forking booking truth\":\n        - cell \"TemporalNormalizationEnvelope\"\n        - cell \"timezone, DST, and clock-skew correctness\"\n        - cell \"prevents supplier-local timestamps from forking booking truth\"\n      - row \"CanonicalSlotIdentity dedupe-safe slot identity and stable tie-break key prevents distinct inventory from collapsing under aliasing\":\n        - cell \"CanonicalSlotIdentity\"\n        - cell \"dedupe-safe slot identity and stable tie-break key\"\n        - cell \"prevents distinct inventory from collapsing under aliasing\"\n      - row \"SlotSetSnapshot frozen searchable and selectable slot set with checksum and recovery posture selection and commit must consume persisted snapshot truth\":\n        - cell \"SlotSetSnapshot\"\n        - cell \"frozen searchable and selectable slot set with checksum and recovery posture\"\n        - cell \"selection and commit must consume persisted snapshot truth\"\n      - row \"SlotSnapshotRecoveryState renderable vs partial vs stale vs no-supply vs support-fallback view state empty results are not enough to imply no supply\":\n        - cell \"SlotSnapshotRecoveryState\"\n        - cell \"renderable vs partial vs stale vs no-supply vs support-fallback view state\"\n        - cell \"empty results are not enough to imply no supply\"\n      - row \"RankPlan and CapacityRankProof frontier-safe rank plan, proof, explanations, and patient cue law keeps ordering stable across pagination, grouping, and replay\":\n        - cell \"RankPlan and CapacityRankProof\"\n        - cell \"frontier-safe rank plan, proof, explanations, and patient cue law\"\n        - cell \"keeps ordering stable across pagination, grouping, and replay\"\n      - row \"OfferSession selected candidate, proof hash, and interaction TTL over pre-ranked offers OfferSession.expiresAt is not proof of exclusivity\":\n        - cell \"OfferSession\"\n        - cell \"selected candidate, proof hash, and interaction TTL over pre-ranked offers\"\n        - cell \"OfferSession.expiresAt is not proof of exclusivity\"\n      - row \"ReservationTruthProjection sole authority for exclusivity, truthful-nonexclusive, pending-confirmation, release, and expiry language selected means held is explicitly forbidden\":\n        - cell \"ReservationTruthProjection\"\n        - cell \"sole authority for exclusivity, truthful-nonexclusive, pending-confirmation, release, and expiry language\"\n        - cell \"selected means held is explicitly forbidden\"\n      - row \"BookingTransaction append-only commit chain with local, processing, external, and authoritative states appointment rows or accepted processing alone may not imply booked truth\":\n        - cell \"BookingTransaction\"\n        - cell \"append-only commit chain with local, processing, external, and authoritative states\"\n        - cell \"appointment rows or accepted processing alone may not imply booked truth\"\n      - row \"BookingConfirmationTruthProjection sole audience-safe authority for booked summary, manage, artifact, and reminder exposure async or disputed confirmation must stay first-class and same-shell\":\n        - cell \"BookingConfirmationTruthProjection\"\n        - cell \"sole audience-safe authority for booked summary, manage, artifact, and reminder exposure\"\n        - cell \"async or disputed confirmation must stay first-class and same-shell\"\n      - row \"AppointmentMan